Most of you guys started following me for my hair tours I used to do so that you can get hair appointments. Some of you know I was one of the first hairstylist that went city to city doing my styles on other women all over the world. I’ve traveled to 36 cities, 3 different countries and my talent and skills has allowed me to do that. I didn’t know why God was allowing me to travel like a “Star” and touch so many people internally while doing it. It was never just about the hair for me. Certain People will sit in my chair, and I will speak to their soul. They will say I was feeding their soul… so then they will look for me to come to their city not to just get their hair done, but their souls fed too.
People Dm me regularly and tell me I changed their life just by giving them a word that they needed at the time. I never could remember what I will say to people and why they will say I changed their life… I simply was just do me But now I know that most of the time God was speaking through me for them. Most will say, they prayed for someone and God sent me. I wasn’t aligned back then how I am now, so I didn’t get it. But now I do. 
Fast forward, in 2020, he sat me down. Stripped me from all things material. My page was hacked. I lost everything!!! And all the people that I thought I needed Just so he can get my attention and I can hear him clearly. I thought it was happening to me, but it was only happening for me so that I can take on this huge mission that he has for me. 
I went into depression for 9 months, lost myself, but while trying to build myself up, I went to life-coaching school, became a certified life coach, took mental health classes and became a mental health advocate and really found out who I really am in the mist of it all. All those things I did for myself help me to become better. And I understand now why he took me through that phase. 
He stripped everything away from me because of the assignment he has for me. 
It was like….
how can I go on an help women and guide them if I never really been through something’s. So he showed me what it was like to fall and get back up, and experience is what I needed to move with this project.! Email me!
